      1185,
      1323,
      1292
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nNA_1 = \\sqrt{1^2 + 5^2 + (-3)^2} = \\sqrt{35}; \\quad NA_2 = \\sqrt{\\left(\\frac{118}{35} - 7\\right)^2 + \\left(-\\frac{57}{7} - 10\\right)^2 + \\left(\\frac{241}{35} + 4\\right)^2} \\approx 21,5.\n$$"
  },
